Luclin Server</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#33333><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=quiksilver1>Quiksilver1</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Forum Wizard</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>3/14/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>7:23:29 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Have hope</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I remember the change from 34 to 39, it's one of the most disappointing in a wizards career, the only thing you really get at 39 is chill sight(which I feel should be a lower lvl spell, mages hand out cold stones at lower levels) and the completion of our port spells. Other than that, the DD for 39 is less than would be expected.  44 however is a great leap with a 600 point DD (over 200 points from the 39) and 49 you get Rend (a 700 point) and the coveted ice comet (whopping 1100).<br>
<br>
They do need to revamp our mana/damage ratios though, they are out of whack for being the &quot;specialty&quot; of our class, hell druids are even equal or better taxi's than us, but apparently that's all I'm good for nowadays.  Let's see, in the last few patches they've nerfed the dagger of frost, nerfed bind/shifting sight, nerfed our entire class with velious, and nerfed us in the PoF and PoH by putting velious caliber mobs in there, I just pray that cazic skin drops off someone other than cazic now otherwise we're not getting any epics (like our epic is that good to begin with, sucky resists on it, and the effect should be for melee's, we're not supposed to be magic shields last I checked since as meat shields we suck).  Obviously a wizard is a support class, however so are clerics and enchanters.  When I was starting out as a wizard, I asked some people what our purpose was (a higher level wizard) they told me it was crowd control by death instead of mez, you protect the tanks by lowering mobs through berserk or enrage stages and also provide an escape route if you can't nuke enough mobs down quick enough.  Basically we were an emergency handle to be pulled, in case of too many mobs, have wizard kill off 1 or 2, thus severely reducing the problem, but then the wizard pays a huge downtime as a result.  Well, now I might as well put a big sign on that says TAXI cause I now charge for ports regularly, might as well make some money while I'm being useless!!  (lets me twink my melee'er (<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  that's what I call KARMA!!<br>
